Package org.stuntaz.libqcw.blobs.barchart

Support for parsing and writing bar charts.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ILineBlob Interface to be implemented by all line types.
IStudyBlob Interface to be implemented by all study types.
 

Class Summary
BarChartBlob Represents a bar chart section in a QCW/QCL file.
BarChartSectionBlob Represents a bar chart section.
BarChartWrapperBlob A thin wrapper containing the core bar chart data structure TODO: BarChartWrapperBlob remove this layer as all that's here is the bar chart blob
BasicLineBlob Represents a basic line drawn on a bar chart.
LineHeaderBlob Represents a line header.
StudyHeaderBlob Represents a header section for a bar chart study.
StudyLayoutBlob Represents the layout characteristics for a study.
StudyLineGroupBlob Represents a group of lines associated with a bar chart study.
SymbolEntryBlob Represents a symbol entry that exists within a study.
UnsupportedLineBlob Represents a currently unsupported line type.
UnsupportedStudyBlob Represents a currently unsupported study type.
VolumeStudyBlob Represents a volume study, including potential Volume substudies.
